invalid type: string "Grocery and Perishable Goods\nGrocery items, fresh food, beverages, and other perishable goods are eligible for refund only when:\n\n- The item arrived spoiled, damaged, or past the stated freshness date.\n- The customer reports the issue within 48 hours of delivery.\n- Photographic evidence of the product and packaging is provided.\n\nted i64 original payment’-+’’’’’’’’’’’’